{% comment %}
  THE RUB — OUR STORY
{% endcomment %}
<section id="story" class="wrap">
  <div class="section-head">
    <span class="tape dark">Our story</span>
    <h2>Kitchen, not a lab.</h2>
  </div>
  <p style="max-width:64ch; font-size:17px; line-height:1.75; color:#3a3324;">
    We tried building this brand as a science experiment once &mdash; molecule logo, lab coats, the whole bit.
    Turns out the truest version was already sitting in the fridge: a deli tub, a strip of painter's tape,
    and a name that didn't need explaining. So we kept the part that mattered &mdash; testing every batch until
    it was right &mdash; and dropped the part that didn't.
  </p>
</section>
